### Ingest a demo document
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/ingest
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "content": "# Agentic RAG\nRAG combines retrieval and generation.",
  "filename": "demo.md",
  "source": "demo.md"
}

### Ingest a local file with Docling
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/ingest/file
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=boundary

--boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="source"

golang工程师.pdf
--boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="golang工程师.pdf"
Content-Type: application/pdf

< ./golang工程师.pdf
--boundary--

### Chat query
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/chat
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "query": "什么是RAG？",
  "top_k": 5
}

### Chat stream (SSE)
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/chat/stream
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: text/event-stream

{
  "query": "什么是RAG？",
  "top_k": 5
}
